 "\n5-sig (E1)=(m+1,2 m+1,3 m+3):\nm = 4 k  -- -----u=5^k--------> (1, 1 + 2 \
k, 3)-- -> III\nm = 4 k + 1 -- -----u=5^k--------> (2, 3 + 2 k, 6)-- -> I0^*\n\
 m = 4 k + 2 -- -----u=5^k--------> (3, 5 + 2 k, 9)-- -> III^*\n m = 4 k  +3  \
 -- ---------> (4, 7 + 2 k, 12)   -- u=5^(k+1)-----> (0, 1+2 k, 0)-- -> I0"
}], "Subsubsection",
