 "\n5-sig (E1)=(m+1,2 m+2+n,3 m+3):\nm = 4 k  -- -----u=5^k--------> (1, 2 + \
2 k+n, 3)-- -> III\nm = 4 k + 1 -- -----u=5^k--------> (2, 4 + 2 k+n, 6)-- -> \
I0^*\n m = 4 k + 2 -- -----u=5^k--------> (3, 6 + 2 k+n, 9)-- -> III^*\n m = \
4 k  +3   -- ---------> (4, 8 + 2 k+n, 12)   -- u=5^(k+1)-----> (0, 2+2 k+n, \
0)-- -> I0"
}], "Subsubsection",
