 "\n5-sig (E5)=(m+1,2 m+2,3 m+3):\nm = 4 k  -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (1, 2 + \
2 k, 3)-- -> III\nm = 4 k + 1 -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (2, 4 + 2 k, 6)-- -> \
