 "\n5-sig (E5)=(m+1,2 m+1+n,3 m+3):\nm = 4 k  -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (1, 1+ \
2 k+n, 3)-- -> III\nm = 4 k + 1 -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (2, 3 + 2 k+n, 6)-- \
-> I0^*\n m = 4 k + 2 -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (3, 5 + 2 k+n, 9)-- -> III^*\n \
