  "d510f9f8-c061-484d-b4c1-367c05f51933"],
 "\n5-sig (E10)=(m+1,2 m+2,3 m+3):\nm = 4 k  -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (1, 2 + \
2 k, 3)-- -> III\nm = 4 k + 1 -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (2, 4 + 2 k, 6)-- -> \
I0^*\n m = 4 k + 2 -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (3, 6 + 2 k, 9)-- -> III^*\n m = \
4 k  +3   -- ---------> (4, 8 + 2 k, 12)   -- u=5^(k+2)-----> (0, 1+2 k, 0)-- \
-> I0"
}], "Subsubsection",
