Cell["\<\

m = 4 k  -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (1, 2 + 2 k, 3)-- -> III
m = 4 k + 1 -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (2, 4 + 2 k, 6)-- -> I0^*
 m = 4 k + 2 -- -----u=5^k+1--------> (3, 6 + 2 k, 9)-- -> III^*
 m = 4 k  +3   -- ---------> (4, 8 + 2 k, 12)   -- u=5^(k+2)-----> (0, 1+2 k, \
0)-- -> I0\
\>", "Text",
